Package fr.flowarg.flowupdater.versions

This package contains all the classes related to the versions.

See: Description

    Interface Description
    IModLoaderVersion  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractForgeVersion
    The base object of a forge version.
    FabricVersion
    The object that contains Fabric's stuff.
    FabricVersion.FabricVersionBuilder
    Builder for FabricVersion.
    ForgeVersionBuilder
    Builder for AbstractForgeVersion
    IModLoaderVersion.ModLoaderLauncherEnvironment
    This class represents a process' environment with a working directory and the launch command.
    NewForgeVersion
    Represent a new Forge version (1.12.2-14.23.5.2851 to 1.18.1)
    OldForgeVersion
    Represent an old Forge version (1.7 to 1.12.2) (No support for versions older than 1.7)
    VanillaVersion  
    VanillaVersion.VanillaVersionBuilder
    A builder for building a vanilla version like FlowUpdater.FlowUpdaterBuilder
